Title: Endgame
Plot: The Stargate is stolen, leading SG-1 to discover that the Trust has taken control of an advanced ship in orbit. Teal'c investigates a series of wide-spread Jaffa deaths.
GuestStars: Ed Anders, Ryan Booth, Chelah Horsdal, Rob Hayter, Barclay Hope, Scott Owen, Benita Ha, Peter Bryant, Lucas Wolf, Gary Jones, Rob Lee, Mark Gibbon, Michael Sorich, Brandy Ledford, Rob Lee
